{
  "stem": "23942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Even though I said Viduy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this went going on-- I remember, it wasn't very long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't remember whether it was a few months or something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we never survived like this, even a year or even half a year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Within that year, we were crouching and hiding and in fields, and everywhere you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was-- it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at that-- no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my grandmother was-- it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe the people who she went into the barn, maybe they gave us some food in the evening, maybe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we couldn't have survived a few months without eating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody can.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was some-- like a potato she would get it from a field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, or some things like grow-- like all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like poppy seeds, you know, grew, and then the, you know, and-- Anyway, so we had something from the fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at night, maybe the people that she-- you know, they allowed her to use the barn, maybe he gave her food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember that part.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I cannot tell you something I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can only remember what I remember clearly, distinctly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as we were crouching, and as we were sort of hiding, she gave us pep talk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She gave us-- we asked, I remember one day, I said Bubbe-- Bubbe-- I used to call her Bubehai-- that's how I called her, Bub-- Bub-- I said, what are we going to do if we don't have food?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said to us, I don't think I'm going to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what she said to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I'm going to make it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you, children, she says, you will probably make it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
